          href="https://www.softnetics.tech/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Softnetics</a
        ></span
      >
    </h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      <time datetime="2024-03-12T17:00:00.000Z">March 13, 2024</time
      >&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<span>Present</span>
    </p>
    <ul class="mb-4 ml-list list-disc marker:text-accent">
      <li>Work with project managers to identify and address any project challenges, keeping things running smoothly</li>
      <li>Partner with designers to align on our vision and ensure seamless implementation</li>
      <li>Engage with everyone (from my teammates to the big boss!) to discuss progress and maintain open lines of communication</li>
